data.text: @THERoyalCrabbit @KensingtonRoyal Yes, yes and yes! This year has been the worst, I want my normal timeline back too. Hopefully everyone will be back soon and we can forget about BS (I like it!) for the next 11 months.

@Laura__Royal @KensingtonRoyal I hope so. I want to hear about engagements, charities, etc. Real news for a change. These last few weeks have been the longest in all of my years of “Balmoral Season.” I tackily refer it to BS.

@Laura__Royal Last year they gave us an update on the autumn plans for the three of them shortly before (a week or so) the first engagements started, which I expect will be in the first full week of September. George starts school again on Thursday 6 September.
@fiamma1990 A chi lo dici! Chissà che finisca questo agosto di "esclusive" per riempire il vuoto, torniamo alla normalità 😉
It was widely reported that her maternity leave would end in September, so the first engagements may be just a few weeks away.
